ce_104ifq1665702843454.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ifq1665702843454.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ifq1665702843454.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ifq1665702843454\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$applproperties \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ifq1665702843454___applproperties_252557\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the presentation properties of the application shell.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__topic_d80405e1_d80406e1_d80407e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__p_d80408e1_d80409e1_d80410e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$applproperties</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>{ <var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertyList</var> }<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertyValuesList</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__section_w252ab1b7b5_w253ab1b7_w254ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__p_d80411e1_d80412e1_d80413e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$applproperties(\"backimage\") = \"backimage=@logo.jpg\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__topic_d52912e1_d52913e1_d52914e1_d52915e1_d52916e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d830959e91\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertiesList</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__3\"> Associative list of application shell\n                        properties</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertyValuesList</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7991e1_d7992e1_d7993e1__entry__3\">Associative list of application shell\n                        properties and their values </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Properties set by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$applproperties</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">Property</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">Technical Name</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">BackColor</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Background color of the window.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">BackImage</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Background image of the window.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">HAlign</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Horizontal alignment of the background image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">HScale</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Horizontal scaling of the background image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">VAlign</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Vertical alignment of background image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">VScale</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Vertical scaling of background image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">PreserveAspect</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Specify whether to preserve the aspect ratio of the background image at\n                        all times.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wjh1665702607394.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wjh1665702607394.html\" title=\"The MessageLine property determines whether the message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window. This is used to display non-obtrusive messages to the user.\">Message Line</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">MessageLine</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">Show or hide the message line at the bottom of the application\n                        window.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">state </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">state</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The application shell window states:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__ul_tcw_vbp_nvb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">NORMAL</code> (default)</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MAXIMIZED</code></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MINIMIZED</code></li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">Left (xpos)</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">XPos</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The left (horizontal) window position, relative to primary Windows\n                        desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">Top (ypos)</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">YPos</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The top (vertical) window position, relative to the primary Windows\n                        desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">Width (xsize)</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">XSize</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The width of the application shell window.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\">Height (ysize)</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">YSize</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The height of the application shell window.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">XPosPerc</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The horizontal application shell window position, as a percentage\n                        relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">YPosPerc</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The vertical window position, as a percentage relative to the relative\n                        to the primary Windows desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">XSizePerc</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The horizontal window size, as a percentage as a percentage relative to\n                        the relative to the primary Windows desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__1\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__2\">YSizePerc</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_jcw_vbp_nvb__entry__3\">The vertical window size, as a percentage relative to the relative to\n                        the primary Windows desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__topic_d52917e1_d52918e1_d52919e1_d52920e1_d52921e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d830959e490\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7997e1_d7998e1_d7999e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$applproperties</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7997e1_d7998e1_d7999e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7997e1_d7998e1_d7999e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Error constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7997e1_d7998e1_d7999e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7997e1_d7998e1_d7999e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1110\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7997e1_d7998e1_d7999e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n UPROCERR_TOPIC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifq1665702843454__table_d7997e1_d7998e1_d7999e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Topic name not known. Invalid property specified.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__topic_d52922e1_d52923e1_d52924e1_d52925e1_d52926e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d830959e547\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__d6512e20\">Use only in Application Shell and Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__topic_d52927e1_d52928e1_d52929e1_d52930e1_d52931e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d830959e556\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__p_d80429e1_d80430e1_d80431e1\">Property values set using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$applproperties</span> override those set in the initialization file with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Shell</span> definition, or values set in the application shell definition.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__section_igy_xzq_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d830959e571\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$applproperties</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ifq1665702843454__pre_tfk_yzq_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vProps = \"\"\nputitem/id vProps, \"backimage\",\"@logo.png\"\nputitem/id vProps, \"PreserveAspect\",\"true\"\n$applproperties() = vProps</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yga1665702577055.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$applname</a><p>Return the name of the Application Shell.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qfx1665702843526.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$appltitle</a><p>Return or set the window title bar text of a Uniface Windows application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gma1665702671256.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Shell</a><p>Sets the default window properties of the application shell.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$applproperties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $applproperties Set the presentation properties of the application shell. $applproperties ( { PropertyList } ) = PropertyValuesList Example: $applproperties(\"backimage\") = \"backimage=@logo.jpg\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description PropertiesList String Associative list of application shell properties PropertyValuesList String Associative list of application shell properties and their values Table 2. Properties set by $applproperties Property Technical Name Description Background Color (BackColor) BackColor Background color of the window. Background Image (BackImage) BackImage Background image of the window. Horizontal Alignment (Halign) HAlign Horizontal alignment of the background image. Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) HScale Horizontal scaling of the background image. Vertical Alignment ( Valign) VAlign Vertical alignment of background image. Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) VScale Vertical scaling of background image. Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) PreserveAspect Specify whether to preserve the aspect ratio of the background image at all times. Message Line MessageLine Show or hide the message line at the bottom of the application window. state state The application shell window states: NORMAL (default) MAXIMIZED MINIMIZED Left (xpos) XPos The left (horizontal) window position, relative to primary Windows desktop. Top (ypos) YPos The top (vertical) window position, relative to the primary Windows desktop. Width (xsize) XSize The width of the application shell window. Height (ysize) YSize The height of the application shell window. XPosPerc The horizontal application shell window position, as a percentage relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop. YPosPerc The vertical window position, as a percentage relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop. XSizePerc The horizontal window size, as a percentage as a percentage relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop. YSizePerc The vertical window size, as a percentage relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop. Return Values Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $applproperties Value Error constant Meaning -1110 UPROCERR_TOPIC Topic name not known. Invalid property specified. Use Use only in Application Shell and Form components. Description Property values set using $applproperties override those set in the initialization file with the Shell definition, or values set in the application shell definition. Example: Using $applproperties vProps = \"\" putitem/id vProps, \"backimage\",\"@logo.png\" putitem/id vProps, \"PreserveAspect\",\"true\" $applproperties() = vProps Copy Related Links $applname Return the name of the Application Shell. $appltitle Return or set the window title bar text of a Uniface Windows application. Shell Sets the default window properties of the application shell. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}